    "Of the 854 research articles initially identified (depicted in Figure 1), we applied Boolean AND filters to refine the selection.",
    "Consequently, 305 articles, spanning from 2016 to 2023, were earmarked for in-depth analysis.",
    "To enhance the meta-analysis aspect, each selected article was subjected to a systematic evaluation based on specific criteria: relevance to the subject, methodological soundness and contribution to the field.",
    "The statistical analysis involved synthesising data points such as study outcomes, methodologies and results to quantitatively assess trends and traditional photography.",
    "Imaging spectroscopy captures intrinsic information in the form of images by revealing information about the target in the whole electromagnetic spectrum."
